      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tadeh̅ gohdinajeet te tumia/ bet pehz ilgu Laiku tap̄ tee atkah̅ peemekleti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Mo Semmes Galla dsir. dam meh̅ Dseefinas/ par Goh- du tamt Taifnam. Bet man jafakka: Es tohpu leefs/ es toh- pu leefs/ waj man! Tee Pahr- kahpaji pahrkahpj/ un ar Pahr- kahpschannu pahrkahpj tee Pahr- kahpaji.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Isbihjafchana/ un Bedre/ un Walgs pahr tew tu Eedsih- wotajs tahs Semmes.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un kas no tahs Isbihja- fchanas Balfs behgs/ tas krit- tihs Bedrê. Un kas no Bedres uskahps/ tas taps Walgâ faguh- stihts. Jo tee Lohgi tahs Aug- stibas irr atwehrti/ un tahs Semmes Patatti trihze.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta Semme tohp laufiht lausita/ ta Semme plihfin plih- fihs/ ta Semme taps kustinata ar leelu Kustinafchannu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta Semme straipatehs ka weens Pcedsehris/ un swalsit- sees ka weena Buhdika/ un win- nas Pahrkahpschana buhs gruh- ta pahr winnu/ un winna krit- tihs un ne zelfees waits aug- scham.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tai Deena peemeklehs tas KUNGS to Augstajo Kar- ra-Spehku Augstibā/ un tohs Kehnixus wirs Semmes.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee taps kehpa fapul- zinatt/ itt ka Zeetumneeki weenā Bedrê/ un taps atsflehgti Zee-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas Mehnes kaunejeeß/ un ta Saule taps Kaunā/ kad tas KUNGS Zebaot waldb̄ us Zianas Kalnu un Jerusale- mê/ un preckich faweem Wezza- jeim buhs Gohdiba.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta XXV. Nodalla.\nEsaijus pateiz Deewam/ ka wiꞥſch fawu fane schu Eenaideekus nogabſis i. Un toh̅ nabbagus Paganus prenehmis: 3. Un ap- raksta tahs daudskahrtigas Labdarischanas tahs Walstibas Kristus : 6.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "KUNGS/ tu effi mans Deews/ tewi gribbu es pa-augstinaht/ es fla- weschu tawu Wahrdn/ jo tu dar- ri brühnigas Leetas. Tawi Pa- dohni no fennenes irr Pateeff- ba un Peetizziba.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo tu effi no ta Pilsfah- ta weenu Afimina-Kohpu Dar- rijs/ to stipru Pilsfahtu par weenn fafrittufschu Kohpu/ tohs skaistus Namming to Swetchi- necku/ ka tas wairs Pilsfahts ne irr/ wiꞥſch ne taps uszelts muhscham.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tapehz flauehs tew twee- na stipra Tauta/ tas Pilsfahts warreno Lauschu tew bihtees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo tu effi tam Nabbagaim weens Stiprums/ weens Stip- ruuns tam Waijadsgam eeksch winna Behdabin/ weena Gelbe- fchana no Pinhdeem/ weens Pa- wehnis prett to Karstinmu/ kad to Breesmitgo Gars (zeltahs) ka Pluhdi prett tahdn Seenu.\n"
    }
  ],
